egory determines the event type. Send the standard name closest to your action for documentation, but the platform will not branch on it. - LinkedIn: ignored. The conversion rule&#39;s &#x60;type&#x60; (LEAD, PURCHASE, etc.) is locked to the destination at rule-creation time. Send the standard name for documentation; LinkedIn does not branch on it. 
